@baseUrl = http://localhost:5177
@token = <paste_service_or_user_jwt>

### Create empty file collection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/collections
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List files in collection
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/collections/{{collectionId}}/files
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Upload into collection (multipart — use Swagger or Postman for file body)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/collections/{{collectionId}}/files
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Upload standalone file
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get file metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Download file
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete file
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete collection (and DB rows; S3 objects removed in service)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/collections/{{collectionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
